388
00:29:01,565 --> 00:29:03,563
Shouldn't we be turning?
We're drifting again.

389
00:29:03,664 --> 00:29:06,247
Not yet. I wasn't
kidding about those fumes.

390
00:29:06,348 --> 00:29:08,872
This can has one or
two good thrusts left...

391
00:29:09,079 --> 00:29:10,497
