00:32:00,187 --> 00:32:01,735
You're gonna make it, Ryan.

420
00:32:03,215 --> 00:32:04,265
No!

421
00:32:25,876 --> 00:32:29,317
I had you. I had you! I had you.

422
00:32:45,035 --> 00:32:46,474
Ryan, do you hear me?

