00:32:53,354 --> 00:32:56,733
My CO2 alarm went off. - Look,
you need to board the station.

425
00:32:57,622 --> 00:32:59,262
Do you see the airlock?

426
00:33:08,531 --> 00:33:11,687
Hey, Ryan, you copy?

427
00:33:14,011 --> 00:33:15,627
Look for the
airlock.

